Wakame-vdc is an IaaS (Infrastructure as a Service) cloud computing framework allowing you to manage a heterogeneous virtualization infrastructure.

Think of Wakame-vdc as a Virtual Data center.

Wakame-vdc can be managed via the native web interface, a cli, or the wakame-vdc API.


